room_title: Escape room "Santa's Workshop Head-to-Head Adventure" by NWA Escape Room in Fayetteville (AR)
room_description: The Grinch is Back! Santa's workshop has been sabotaged and only you can save the day and keep all the girls and boys from being disappointed on Christmas! Can you think outside the box and use all your wits to undo the Grinch's scheme, find the missing toys and save Christmas?
